<h3>The Only Meme Coins Worth Holding in a Bear Market</h3>
<p>Most meme coins will never recover from a bear market. The 2022 bear market killed 99% of meme coins launched in 2021. The ones that survived (DOGE, SHIB) had: massive communities, real utility or brand recognition, multiple exchange listings, and development teams that stayed active.</p>

<p>For the 2025-2026 cycle, the meme coins most likely to survive and thrive in the next bull run are DOGE, SHIB, PEPE, WIF, BONK, and FLOKI ” each backed by communities and market caps that have proven resilient across cycles.</p>

